videos.description: Off the missed free throw, Zack McRoberts dives to make the save by tossing the ball to Curtis Jones, who makes the instant no-look pass to Thomas Bryant for the Indiana two-hand slam.
videos.headline: Diving save and a no-look pass leads to huge dunk
